genresAdvancedInfo.name: rock catarinense
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Hailing from Santa Catarina, Brazil, rock catarinense is a genre that blends traditional rock with elements of Brazilian music. It often features catchy guitar riffs and lyrics in Portuguese that touch on themes such as love, politics, and social issues.
